### ============================================================
### AUTH API - REST Client Testing
### ============================================================
### Base URL — sesuaikan jika port berbeda
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

### Catatan alur terbaru:
### - Register sekolah/mitra akan menghasilkan account_status=pending dan is_active=false.
### - Admin harus approve dulu via requests/admin-registrations.http sebelum login sekolah/mitra berhasil.

### ============================================================
### 1. REGISTER SEKOLAH
###    Endpoint : POST /api/auth/register
###    Butuh file: requests/sample-files/logo.jpg
###                requests/sample-files/document.pdf
###                image_1..image_5 opsional
### ============================================================

# @name registerSekolah
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BoundaryKOMPETA

--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="role"

sekolah
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="email"

smk.negeri1@example.com
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="password"

password123
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="password_confirmation"

password123
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="school_name"

SMK Negeri 1 Contoh
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="npsn"

12345678
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="accreditation"

A
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="address"

Jl. Pendidikan No. 1, Jakarta Selatan
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="expertise_fields[]"

RPL
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="expertise_fields[]"

TKJ
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="short_description"

SMK unggulan yang berfokus pada teknologi informasi dan komunikasi.
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="logo"; filename="logo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-files/logo.jpg
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image_1"; filename="school-image-1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-files/logo.jpg
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image_2"; filename="school-image-2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-files/logo.jpg
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="operational_license"; filename="izin-operasional.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./sample-files/document.pdf
--BoundaryKOMPETA--

###

### ============================================================
### 2. REGISTER MITRA - PERUSAHAAN (PT/CV)
###    Endpoint : POST /api/auth/register
###    Butuh file: requests/sample-files/document.pdf
###                requests/sample-files/logo.jpg
### ============================================================

# @name registerMitraPerusahaan
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=BoundaryKOMPETA

--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="role"

mitra
--BoundaryKOMPETA
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="mitra_type"

